snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 Phantom Liberty - Gameplay Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Check out the latest trailer for the highly anticipated Phantom Liberty expansion for Cyberpunk 2077. We're getting new cyberware, new weapons – including a WARHAMMER – and new perks that will make this already-deep RPG even deeper. You can play Cyberpunk 2077 Phantom Liberty on September 26, 2023 on Xbox Series X | S, PS5 and PC.
